Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name! I said I'd remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shindou Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou... Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:00.72,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carve it into my mind too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.94,Background,,0,0,0,,the name of Shindou Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:14.99,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(355,115)}The Thirty-Seventh Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:14.99,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}The Pro Exam Begins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai... it's finally time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:41.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to become pro... to catch up to Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:05.67,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs27.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\fad(584,626)\pos(320,357)}Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:12.96,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs27.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\fad(584,626)\pos(320,357)}First Match
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.33,Sai,,0,0,0,,Calm down Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? You're all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we're all just as nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can put the drinks we bought\Ninto this fridge right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think I can put bread in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't call someone older than you directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki... san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the guy Shindou was scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad you made it to the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I look at it, you're\Ncuter than Kawai-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kawai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's someone that always does this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!? Do it to that Kawai guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it to Kawai-san. He's too scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tsubaki-san's a lot better\Nat Go than Kawai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to playing you.\NI have to take another win from ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.36,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're talking back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:01.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou's changed since the preliminaries...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. If you're going to order a lunch,\Nplease place your order here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.70,Background,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please place your order by 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom packed me a lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! You don't seem scared\Nof the bearded man anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe, actually I used him to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.78,Sai,,0,0,0,,That's a huge improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the match hall early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:06:02.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The finals is a round robin tournament that\Nmeets three times a week on Sundays, Tuesdays,\Nand Saturdays for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There are 28 participants this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.64,Sai,,0,0,0,,Are we deciding today's opponent by lottery again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Only the top three pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.17,Sai,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the guy I lost to during the preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru's attitude has changed\Nsignificantly from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:41.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you're trembling with excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:51.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,Your confidence in being able to\Nbring out all of your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:54.84,Sai,,0,0,0,,the way you did against Su-Young\Nis making you yearn for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,In a wish to test your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Iijima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you passed the preliminaries\Nwith a win by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I just barely passed. Passing\Nis passing. It's no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:20.10,Background,,0,0,0,,It's time, so please gather in the Match Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll begin drawing lots now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.27,Background,,0,0,0,,Please come up here once you've been called.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:31.73,Background,,0,0,0,,Nakamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.46,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura-kun's number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold onto your sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.88,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:53.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You only draw lots on the first day. The\Ntournament chart's already been filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm number 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:08:00.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Once your number has been decided. Your opponents\Nfor the entire exam are decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm playing Iijima-san on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Set your game clocks to three hours each. Clock\Ncount is a minute per move.\NKomi is set to 5.5 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.81,Background,,0,0,0,,Please begin then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I should place the order for the lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:10.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Not even five minutes passed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Calm down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(455,132)}Japanese Go Research Center
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't happen in any normal match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The pro exam really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first day, there's so much tension\Nin the air, I can't bear to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the lounge on the second floor until lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:09.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My goal isn't to just pass. It's to pass in first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:15.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's begun. The long long pro exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Only three people will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This year I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}He's calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is it because he's playing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:40.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Or is it because he's used to the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose on the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The pro exam only happens once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time, so please halt your clocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for lunch! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! Lunch! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're full of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They look more like best friends than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's because we went to the Go salons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go salons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san and I took him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he had never played\Nat a Go salon before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the fuck did you do that?\NWhy did you make your rival stronger!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Morishita always says that people who will\Nbecome strong will become strong no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't have to help him\Nright before the pro exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher even says that I've become\Nmuch stronger since Shindou started\Ncoming to the study sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It seems like taking care of\NShindou's made you stronger too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing really well right now. I can tell myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pass this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the pairings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.89,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs27.5\fsp8\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\frz17\move(192,16,259,89)}Pro Exam Pairings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:23.89,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs27.5\fsp8\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\frz17\pos(259,89)}Pro Exam Pairings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.82,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm playing Shindou at...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,wow it's towards the end. The day before the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, I'll be playing you\Non the thirteenth match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got them right in a row. Shindou on the\Ntwelfth match, you on the thirteenth match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"You made your rival stronger... Are you stupid..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shindou passes and we fail,\Nwe may just be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:13.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There are 27 matches total, I can't\Nbe getting excited over one win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:18.79,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru... it seems you've taken another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:25.34,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs21.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\fad(584,0)\pos(320,362)}Second Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Second quarter began in school before I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:57.79,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs26.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\fad(584,0)\pos(320,360)}Third Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Win by 6.5 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:21.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So far, the only undefeated people are Isumi-san,\Nand me, and Waya, and...  Shindou too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My goal is to pass with no losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.45,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\1c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\fad(0,834)\pos(320,362)}Sixth Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.33,Background,,0,0,0,,Four people with six straight wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, and Ochi, and Waya, and Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya's doing well. Even you lost right\NHonda-kun? Well, I lost too but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand Isumi-san and Ochi's\Nsix straight wins, but Shindou too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just started. Even if you've lost six straight\Ngames, you can pass if you win all the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, all wins isn't all good. You\Nmight lose one game and collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay I'm going to close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All wins isn't good? Of course it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading for all wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him!? It's just starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I doubt Shindou will\Ncontinue winning for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.11,Background,,0,0,0,,Iijima-kun, you played Shindou\Non the first game right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He played a calm game, I got nervous so I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out once you play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:15.35,Background,,0,0,0,,Over here, it's tougher on white if you simply go to\Nthe kosumi instead of attacking him with a Keima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.68,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasoki 7dan is easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday's Kigirai 8dan was horrible at teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder when it was that you learned Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one paying pros to come\Nand play tutoring games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you learned Go by watching me\Nplay, and you passed me quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, calling the pros is all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, can you bring me a whiskey and water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:00.48,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that my grandson's\Naiming to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:05.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Your father was no good. He\Ndidn't even touch the stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you practice at Go salons. I'll even\Nhave the pros come teach you every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how much it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the pro exams? Do you think\Nyou can pass with the top score?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan on doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed Isumi-san and was first place on the\Nlast Insei rankings before the pro exams too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, all the pros coming here have\Nbeen set for this entire week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe we should get Touya\N2dan come sometime next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya 2 dan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's passed with the top score last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:47.11,Background,,0,0,0,,Your pro exam will go on, so he can\Nprobably give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's probably better to listen to a young person\Nabout stuff like that, rather than some old people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:03.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I haven't played Touya 2 dan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:08.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's a great opportunity. I wanted to play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:16.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Once I become pro, we'll both be lower dan players.\NHe's a rival that I may be playing immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.19,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\move(314,184,314,33)}Pro Examination
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.19,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\move(315,253,315,103)}Scores
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Six straight wins!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou... Shindou has six straight wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:38.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even if he has six straight wins, the pro exams\Nare long, six wins isn't very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:48.29,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(166,204)}7 Insei  Shindou Hikaru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:46.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But it's true that only four people are undefeated\Nso far. Shindou is one of those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:53.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Tell me... tell me exactly how strong he is right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:57.72,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(185,184)}7 Insei  Shindou Hikaru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.10,Background,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, it's a phone call for\Nyou from the Go Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Going to someone's house to tutor them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... no. It's not that I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But could you turn them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to focus on my own studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Insei!? I'll be tutoring an Insei!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone taking the exam right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes please set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a look at how\Nstrong you are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're explaining Go terms again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you place your stone immediately next\Nto another stone, it's called a "Tsuke"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you play diagonally to a Tsuke\Nlike this, it's called a "Hane"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you place a stone next to the "tsuke"\Nstone after a "hane" is a "Nobi"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's say black connects these two isolated\Nstones, this is called a "Tsugi"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If black doesn't play there, and white plays\Nthere instead, cutting the two stones\Napart, this move is called a "Kiri"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Once you learn Go terms, you'll be able to\Nunderstand what Sai talks about, and explanations,\Nand Go will become even more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:01.32,Background,,0,0,0,,I want to find out how strong Shindou is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:05.99,Background,,0,0,0,,You don't think I can beat Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:09.28,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou will trip along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:12.20,Background,,0,0,0,,Sorry but I'm going to beat you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:24.72,Background,,0,0,0,,He lost!? To who!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.62,intro_credit,,0,0,0,,{\fad(144,0)\bord3\3c&H000000&\c&HE0E1E5&\move(325,21,325,144,19,135)}Elite-Fansubs
